sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / API Client
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as odh-model-controller<br/>Webhook (9443/TCP TLS)
    participant Controller as odh-model-controller<br/>Reconciler
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>(HAProxy) 443/TCP
    participant IstioGW as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>8443/TCP
    participant Predictor as KServe Predictor Pod
    participant NGC as NVIDIA NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry<br/>HTTP/HTTPS

    Note over User,Predictor: Flow 1: KServe Serverless InferenceService Deployment

    User->>K8sAPI: POST InferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Mutate/Validate InferenceService<br/>HTTPS/9443, TLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response
    K8sAPI-->>User: InferenceService Created

    Note over Controller: Watch event triggers reconciliation

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create OpenShift Route<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Istio Gateway (port 8445)<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Authorino AuthConfig<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor/PodMonitor<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create PeerAuthentication<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token

    Note over Client,Predictor: Inference Request Flow

    Client->>Router: HTTPS/443 (TLS Passthrough)
    Router->>IstioGW: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS (ISVC serving cert)
    IstioGW->>Predictor: HTTP/HTTPS<br/>mTLS (Istio)<br/>Auth: Authorino AuthConfig

    Note over User,NGC: Flow 2: NIM Account Integration

    User->>K8sAPI: POST NIM Account CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate NIM Account<br/>HTTPS/9443, TLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response

    Note over Controller: Watch event triggers NIM reconciliation

    Controller->>NGC: Validate API Key + Fetch Models<br/>HTTPS/443, NGC API Key
    NGC-->>Controller: Model Configuration
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap, Secret, Template<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token

    Note over Controller,ModelReg: Flow 3: Data Connection & Model Registry

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update storage-config Secret<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    Controller->>ModelReg: Sync InferenceService metadata<br/>HTTP(S), Bearer Token
